name: High-quality Palo Santo incense from Peru, 7 Sticks
description: Palo santo, revered for its purifying properties, is traditionally burned to cleanse and purify spaces of negative energies and to create an environment conducive to meditation and prayer. Its smoke is used to calm the mind and spirit, relieving stress and anxiety, and promoting relaxation and overall well-being. Additionally, it serves as an essential tool during meditation, helping to induce a tranquil and receptive mental state, and is also known for its properties as a natural insect repellent.
